com.itko.lisaint

Class LoggedSql

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.itko.lisaint.LoggedSql
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IReport, java.io.Serializable

    public class LoggedSql
extends java.lang.Object
implements IReport, java.io.Serializable
    A holder class for SQLs issued by the app. Sent back to LISA so that tests can assert that particular SQLs were issued.
    See Also:
